TOPRO TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 42.40% to NT$1,515,000 from NT$2,630,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             1,515            2,630     
YOY%             -42.40%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             5,077            12,413    
YOY%             -59.10% 
=================================================================
 